{
  "stem": "8.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And, my father, eventually, was also called into the labor battalion and he also had to leave.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Now, this is a, a very emotional memory that I have of my father.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He was a man of pale, pale skin, always protected from the sun.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And, he was always gentle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And, as he put his backpack on and I saw him saying goodbye, I had this feeling that I don't think I will ever see him again because, he did not look like he could survive any hardships.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And, indeed, I never saw him after he left.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My, my mother and I stayed in the ghetto and there were many air raids in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "I suppose the air raids came from the Americans, but I'm not sure.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had to go down to the cellar to the shelter when the air raids came.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And it was interesting, because I felt kind of happy being in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And, the reason, because I liked being with people.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I needed the comfort of having other people around me.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And, it felt like a community.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It felt like we were not alone.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It's very hard to appreciate how much that means to people not to be alone when something like this happens.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "I had an interesting experience when I was in the, in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "I-- There was a boy who came to stay with us and one night when there was an air raid we decided not to go down.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And, we watched how the bombs came down and he kissed me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And that was the first time that I was ever kissed, and something that I cannot forget.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
